(18, 3, '<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h2 style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; font-weight: normal; margin-top: 0px; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.6em; margin-left: 0px; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; padding-top: 0.5em; padding-bottom: 0.17em; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-style: solid; border-bottom-color: rgb(170, 170, 170); width: auto; font-size: 19px; font-family: sans-serif; line-height: 19px; ">\r\n	<span class="mw-headline" id="History">History</span></h2>\r\n<div class="rellink relarticle mainarticle" style="font-style: italic; padding-left: 1.6em; margin-bottom: 0.5em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; ">\r\n	Main article:&nbsp;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/History_of_wikis" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="History of wikis" wotsearchprocessed="true">History of wikis</a></div>\r\n<div class="thumb tright" style="clear: right; float: right; margin-bottom: 1.3em; width: auto; margin-top: 0.5em; margin-right: 0px; margin-left: 1.4em; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 19px; ">\r\n	<div class="thumbinner" style="min-width: 100px; border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-left-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-image: initial; padding-top: 3px !important; padding-right: 3px !important; padding-bottom: 3px !important; padding-left: 3px !important; background-color: rgb(249, 249, 249); font-size: 12px; text-align: center; overflow-x: hidden; overflow-y: hidden; width: 222px; ">\r\n		<a class="image" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:HNL_Wiki_Wiki_Bus.jpg" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " wotsearchprocessed="true"><img alt="" class="thumbimage" height="165" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/42/HNL_Wiki_Wiki_Bus.jpg/220px-HNL_Wiki_Wiki_Bus.jpg" style="border-top-style: solid; border-right-style: solid; border-bottom-style: solid; border-left-style: solid; border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; vertical-align: middle; border-top-width: 1px; border-right-width: 1px; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-left-width: 1px; border-top-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-right-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-bottom-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); border-left-color: rgb(204, 204, 204); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); " width="220" /></a>\r\n		<div class="thumbcaption" style="text-align: left; border-top-style: none; border-right-style: none; border-bottom-style: none; border-left-style: none; border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial; line-height: 1.4em; padding-top: 3px !important; padding-right: 3px !important; padding-bottom: 3px !important; padding-left: 3px !important; font-size: 11px; ">\r\n			<div class="magnify" style="float: right; border-top-style: none !important; border-right-style: none !important; border-bottom-style: none !important; border-left-style: none !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important; background-image: none !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: initial !important; background-position: initial initial !important; background-repeat: initial initial !important; ">\r\n				<a class="internal" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:HNL_Wiki_Wiki_Bus.jpg" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: initial !important; display: block; border-top-style: none !important; border-right-style: none !important; border-bottom-style: none !important; border-left-style: none !important; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; border-image: initial !important; background-position: initial initial !important; background-repeat: initial initial !important; " title="Enlarge" wotsearchprocessed="true"><img alt="" height="11" src="http://bits.wikimedia.org/skins-1.18/common/images/magnify-clip.png" style="border-top-style: none !important; border-right-style: none !important; border-bottom-style: none !important; border-left-style: none !important; border-width: initial; border-color: initial; border-image: initial !important; vertical-align: middle; display: block; border-width: initial !important; border-color: initial !important; background-image: none !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: initial !important; background-position: initial initial !important; background-repeat: initial initial !important; " width="15" /></a></div>\r\n			<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki_Wiki_Shuttle" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="Wiki Wiki Shuttle" wotsearchprocessed="true">Wiki Wiki Shuttle</a>&nbsp;at&nbsp;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Honolulu_International_Airport" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="Honolulu International Airport" wotsearchprocessed="true">Honolulu International Airport</a></div>\r\n	</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.4em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; ">\r\n	WikiWikiWeb was the first wiki.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-ebersbach10_5-0" style="line-height: 1em; "><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki#cite_note-ebersbach10-5" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; white-space: nowrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " wotsearchprocessed="true">[6]</a></sup>&nbsp;Ward Cunningham started developing WikiWikiWeb in Portland, Oregon, in 1994, and installed it on the&nbsp;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Domain_name" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="Domain name" wotsearchprocessed="true">Internet domain</a><a class="external text" href="http://c2.com/" rel="nofollow" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(102, 51, 102); background-image: url(data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAAoAAAAKCAYAAACNMs+9AAAAGXRFWHRTb2Z0d2FyZQBBZG9iZSBJbWFnZVJlYWR5ccllPAAAAFZJREFUeF59z4EJADEIQ1F36k7u5E7ZKXeUQPACJ3wK7UNokVxVk9kHnQH7bY9hbDyDhNXgjpRLqFlo4M2GgfyJHhjq8V4agfrgPQX3JtJQGbofmCHgA/nAKks+JAjFAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC); background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; padding-right: 13px; background-position: 100% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat; " wotsearchprocessed="true">c2.com</a></p>\r\n<div style="position: relative; visibility: visible; background-image: url(chrome-extension://bhmmomiinigofkjcapegjjndpbikblnp/skin/fusion/16_16/plain/r5.png) !important; background-attachment: initial !important; background-origin: initial !important; background-clip: initial !important; background-color: initial !important; margin-left: 4px !important; display: inline-block; cursor: pointer; width: 16px; height: 16px; background-position: 100% 50%; background-repeat: no-repeat no-repeat !important; " wotsearchtarget="c2.com">\r\n	&nbsp;</div>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-6" style="line-height: 1em; "><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki#cite_note-6" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; white-space: nowrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " wotsearchprocessed="true">[7]</a></sup>&nbsp;on March 25, 1995. It was named by Cunningham, who remembered a&nbsp;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Honolulu_International_Airport" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="Honolulu International Airport" wotsearchprocessed="true">Honolulu International Airport</a>&nbsp;counter employee telling him to take the &quot;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki_Wiki_Shuttle" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="Wiki Wiki Shuttle" wotsearchprocessed="true">Wiki Wiki Shuttle</a>&quot; bus that runs between the airport&#39;s terminals. According to Cunningham, &quot;I chose wiki-wiki as an alliterative substitute for &#39;quick&#39; and thereby avoided naming this stuff quick-web.&quot;<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-cunningham_7-0" style="line-height: 1em; "><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki#cite_note-cunningham-7" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; white-space: nowrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " wotsearchprocessed="true">[8]</a></sup><sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-history_8-0" style="line-height: 1em; "><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki#cite_note-history-8" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; white-space: nowrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " wotsearchprocessed="true">[9]</a></sup></p>\r\n<p>\r\n	&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.4em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; ">\r\n	Cunningham was in part inspired by Apple&#39;s&nbsp;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/HyperCard" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="HyperCard" wotsearchprocessed="true">HyperCard</a>. Apple had designed a system allowing users to create virtual &quot;card stacks&quot; supporting links among the various cards. Cunningham developed&nbsp;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Vannevar_Bush" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="Vannevar Bush" wotsearchprocessed="true">Vannevar Bush&#39;s</a>&nbsp;ideas by allowing users to &quot;comment on and change one another&#39;s text.&quot;<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-Britannica_1-1" style="line-height: 1em; "><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki#cite_note-Britannica-1" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; white-space: nowrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " wotsearchprocessed="true">[2]</a></sup><sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-hypercard_9-0" style="line-height: 1em; "><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki#cite_note-hypercard-9" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; white-space: nowrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " wotsearchprocessed="true">[10]</a></sup></p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.4em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; ">\r\n	In the early 2000s, wikis were increasingly adopted in enterprise as collaborative software. Common uses included project communication, intranets, and documentation, initially for technical users. Today some&nbsp;<a class="mw-redirect" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Corporate_wiki" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="Corporate wiki" wotsearchprocessed="true">companies use wikis</a>&nbsp;as their only collaborative software and as a replacement for static intranets, and some schools and universities use wikis to enhance&nbsp;<a class="mw-redirect" href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Group_learning" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="Group learning" wotsearchprocessed="true">group learning</a>. There may be greater use of wikis behind&nbsp;<a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Firewall_(computing)" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="Firewall (computing)" wotsearchprocessed="true">firewalls</a>&nbsp;than on the public Internet.</p>\r\n<p style="margin-top: 0.4em; margin-right: 0px; margin-bottom: 0.5em; margin-left: 0px; line-height: 19px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; ">\r\n	On March 15, 2007,&nbsp;<i>wiki</i>&nbsp;entered the online&nbsp;<i><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Oxford_English_Dictionary" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " title="Oxford English Dictionary" wotsearchprocessed="true">Oxford English Dictionary</a></i>.<sup class="reference" id="cite_ref-OED1_10-0" style="line-height: 1em; "><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Wiki#cite_note-OED1-10" style="text-decoration: none; color: rgb(11, 0, 128); background-image: none; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: initial; white-space: nowrap; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; " wotsearchprocessed="true">[11]</a></sup></p>\r\n', 11, 'История', 0),
